{
  "description": "A close-up shot of the inner petals and stamens of a deep purple tulip. The petals are softly illuminated with a slight gradient transitioning from a rich purple to a delicate pink at the edges. The stamens are a vibrant golden-yellow with darker orange tips, creating a striking contrast against the dark purple interior.  The background is blurred, with hints of green foliage and out-of-focus bokeh lights adding depth to the image. The focus is very sharp on the stamens and the interior of the tulip, highlighting the intricate details of the flower's reproductive parts.",
